{"tid":1582279,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(9.20) 元朗信義中學便服日「反黑」　","createTime":"2019-09-20T03:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T04:59:16.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b971b26899e00f8270a70dfb176f0ab3f9a14ae5","tid":1582279,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T03:40:34.000Z","msg":"反修例事件後，黑衣成為校園禁忌？基督教香港信義會元朗信義中學學生日前接獲校方廣播通知，指學生於今（20日）的便服日期間，不可穿著全黑套裝，違規者將通知家長將學生接走。今早七時，校園外陸續有穿著便服的學生上學，亦有學生穿著全黑衣物，在校門外集合，準時8時05分齊步走進校園。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3307466/org/26a61a8a9e243f0e53aa7d8617e624c0.jpg/SQiqezdpdBzbzUUeKX0mQrglx7afWTRItVnNBZ9ZzQU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3307466%2Forg%2F26a61a8a9e243f0e53aa7d8617e624c0.jpg%2FSQiqezdpdBzbzUUeKX0mQrglx7afWTRItVnNBZ9ZzQU&h=59d6ee45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據報，早前有元朗信義中學學生在社交媒體上聲稱，自己將會在便服日穿著全黑衣物上學。有家長獲悉事件後，致電校方反映意見，校方亦隨即在校內廣播，指便服日期間，同學只可以選擇黑衣或黑褲其一，並禁止佩戴黑色口罩，否則將會通知家長將違規者接走。有同學指出，學校從來沒有不可穿黑衣褲上學的規例，今次在未有徵詢同學的意見下禁令，做法苛刻。<br />\n<br />\n現場所見，大部分穿著黑色衣物的學生均為高中學生，偶有同學未有理會校方要求，繼續佩戴黑口罩上學。「個個人都有自由揀自己著咩衫，如果驚涉及言論，綠色、藍色衫都唔應該著，而唔單單係黑色唔應該著。」有不願具名的高中同學表示，校方的做法有問題，同學之間亦有就事件討論。受訪期間，有老師及校內牧師在校門守候，並以保護學生為由，召集屋邨保安驅趕傳媒。<br />\n<br />\n校方以負責人不在港為由，對事件暫未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3307467/org/31196f362e8c0ac05ac3abff148f89c7.jpg/42CxHReJCwqpx6At9RdaGuMH3_0aR54t78cXV8XHF1c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3307467%2Forg%2F31196f362e8c0ac05ac3abff148f89c7.jpg%2F42CxHReJCwqpx6At9RdaGuMH3_0aR54t78cXV8XHF1c&h=6191700a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/377349/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E4%BF%A1%E7%BE%A9%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E4%BE%BF%E6%9C%8D%E6%97%A5-%E5%8F%8D%E9%BB%91-%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%A9%BF%E9%BB%91%E8%A1%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%B9%E8%8B%9B%E5%88%BB#media_id=3307467</code></pre>"},{"pid":"901dd8318bde26ddf353f85636af9a498a42d508","tid":1582279,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T03:41:19.000Z","msg":"[公海 文宣整合] 9.29全球反極權集會 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581746\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581746</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9.29 Global Anti Totalitarianism 文宣、資訊、行動整合Channel</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/AntiChinazi929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiChinazi929&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8olS5wRbVpD6X1tjwtO29R8%3D&h=16c35fc3\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AntiChinazi929</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>9.29 Global Anti Totalitarianism 公海</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8olS5wRbVpD6X1tjwtO29R8%3D&h=231712a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ</a>"},{"pid":"d146e990d30988f925e473bf73b074a7f2adce8a","tid":1582279,"uid":49643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:36:39.000Z","msg":"依班中學生有料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e80a91105084c9924e0dcbec4f53319d3a0f35cb","tid":1582279,"uid":49853,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:39:06.000Z","msg":"班家長係咪弱撚智，咁都要投訴"},{"pid":"5e01d71292fc49dae299fb82e946caeb9e6802b8","tid":1582279,"uid":261913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:40:04.000Z","msg":"同學仔夠吉士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9cb27943b66b90875833c7f45e1c89c445454a","tid":1582279,"uid":60709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:43:52.000Z","msg":"呢間野終於出名"},{"pid":"72ede177698fa3c9b179284a16a6dd3609a69018","tid":1582279,"uid":308595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"ci